### Create Attendee Profile
POST {{baseUrl}}/attendees
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
    "user_id": 10,
    "date_of_birth": "1995-08-20",
    "gender": "female",
    "interests": ["music", "fashion"]
}

### Expected Response:
# {
#     "success": true,
#     "message": "Attendee profile created successfully",
#     "data": {
#         "attendee": {...}
#     }
# }

###

### Update Attendee Profile
PUT {{baseUrl}}/attendees/{{attendeeId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
    "gender": "female",
    "interests": ["music", "fashion", "art"]
}

### Expected Response:
# {
#     "success": true,
#     "message": "Attendee profile updated successfully"
# }

###

### Delete Attendee Profile
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/attendees/{{attendeeId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Expected Response:
# {
#     "success": true,
#     "message": "Attendee deleted successfully"
# }

###
